cancellation_reason.description:
Reason of reservation cancellation
- API-ISSUE: Some technical issue with api setting;
- TECHNICAL-ISSUE: Some technical issue;
- MISSING-PASSENGER-INFO: Mandatory information as date of birth, address hotel is missing, therefore provider cannot accept the reservation;
- VENUE-CLOSED: Weather reason, maintenance, strike;
- REJECTED-SCHEDULE-CHANGE: Client did not accept the suggested schedule change;
- REJECTED-ORDER:Rreservation was rejected by provider - overbooking/minimum number of participants not reached/wrong slot uploaded in our system;
- MISSING-MEETING-POINT-DETAILS: Provider did not informed us about change of meeting point/cs did not provide updated information to the final customer;
- GRACE-PERIOD: Time between after booking and canceling without concerns;
- CANCELLED-BY-CUSTOMER: Cancellation performed by customer.
